OFX - OpenFrameworks Management Tool
====================================

Put this script into your OpenFrameworks installation directory
(the one that contains "addons" directory).

Usage
-----

ofx
ofx help
    - print this help

ofx refresh
    - redownload addons list (otherwise it is downloaded just once)


ofx list
    - list all addons

ofx search TEXT
    - search for text in name and description of addons

ofx category
    - list categories of addons

ofx category NAME
    - list all addons in the category

ofx owner
    - list all owners

ofx owner NAME
    - list all addons belonging to owner


ofx info NAME
    - show info about addon

ofx install NAME
    - install addon

ofx reinstall NAME
    - remove and install addon

ofx upgrade NAME
    - upgrade addon (call git pull in its directory)

ofx remove NAME
    - remove addon


